{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2282e","heading":"Post-authorization change reports","label":"2282e Post-authorization change reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/ch36/schV","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Water Resources Development Act of 2016, and also as part of the Water Infrastructure Improvements for the Nation Act, also known as the WIIN Act, and not as part of the Water Resources Development Act of 1986 which comprises this chapter.","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","“Secretary” DefinedSecretary means the Secretary of the Army, see , set out as a note under .section 1002 of Pub. L. 114–322section 2201 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"may not be delayed as a result of consideration being given to changes in policy or priority with respect to project consideration; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the Committee on Environment and Public Works of the Senate; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure of the House of Representatives.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Completion review","label":"b Completion review","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"review the report; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provide to Congress any recommendations of the Secretary regarding modification of the applicable water resources development project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Prior reports","label":"c Prior reports","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 120 days after , with respect to any post-authorization change report that was completed prior to , and is subject to a review by the Secretary that has yet to be completed, the Secretary shall complete review of, and provide recommendations to Congress with respect to, the report.December 16, 2016December 16, 2016","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Post-authorization change report inclusions","label":"d Post-authorization change report inclusions","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a general reevaluation report;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a limited reevaluation report; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2282e/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft33%2Fs2282e%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any other report that recommends the modification of an authorized water resources development project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
